as music concerts. In 2006, the stadium of TSV Hartberg was expanded to that it could seat both home and away visitors with a capacity of 6,000 increasing from 4,500.<ref>http://www.worldstadiums.com/europe/countries/austria.shtml</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bundesliga.at/bewerbe/index.php?PHPSESSID=fe92ca2e378250b2e0a295d0e43e399e&sub1=2&sub2=2_4&sub3=2_4_1&vrnr=8142&PHPSESSID=fe92ca2e378250b2e0a295d0e43e399e |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2010-08-09 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100918135106/http://bundesliga.at/bewerbe/index.php?PHPSESSID=aac4ffc89509bb2d7019a50f1f42172d&sub1=2&sub2=2_4&sub3=2_4_1&vrnr=8142&PHPSESSID=aac4ffc89509bb2d7019a50f1f42172d |archivedate=18 September 2010}}</ref>\n\n==Current squad==\n''Updated 3 November 2019.''\n\n{{Fs start}}\n{{Fs player|no=1  |pos=GK |nat=AUT |name=[[Ren\u00e9 Swete]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=4  |pos=DF |nat=AUT |name=[[Michael Huber]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=6  |pos=DF |nat=AUT |name=[[Andreas Lienhart]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=7  |pos=DF |nat=AUT |name=[[Siegfried Rasswalder]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=8  |pos=MF |nat=AUT |name=[[Christoph Kr\u00f6pfl]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=9  |pos=FW |nat=SVN |name=[[Rajko Rep]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=10 |pos=MF |nat=AUT |name=[[Stefan Rakowitz]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=11 |pos=MF |nat=AUT |name=[[Lukas Gabbichler]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=14 |pos=DF |nat=AUT |name=[[Christian Klem]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=15 |pos=MF |nat=AUT |name=Marcel Schantl}}\n{{Fs player|no=16 |pos=MF |nat=AUT |name=Nino K\u00f6pf}}\n{{Fs player|no=18 |pos=MF |nat=AUT |name=[[David Cancola]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=19 |pos=FW |nat=CZE |name=[[Tom\u00e1\u0161 Ostr\u00e1k]]|other=on loan from [[1. FC K\u00f6ln]]}}\n{{Fs mid}}\n{{Fs player|no=20 |pos=MF |nat=BEN |name=[[Jodel Dossou]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=21 |pos=GK |nat=AUT |name=[[Florian Faist]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=22 |pos=DF |nat=MLI |name=Amadou Dante}}\n{{Fs player|no=23 |pos=DF |nat=AUT |name=[[Tobias Kainz]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=24 |pos=FW |nat=AUT |name=[[Dario Tadi\u0107]]}}\